reviews.text: Very nice ice creams there, esp chocolate. My friend bought the hazelnut spread and apparently that’s also very good.
Very good. Finally an ice-cream shop which offer Pistachio ice-cream! The service is very good and very kind... They let me take a cup when they have just closed! Thanks!
The gelato is life changing!! Chocolate is the best (duh, Captain Obvious).
Complete rip off!! Ordered the 2 scoop mini for $55, it was literally 2 tablespoons of ice cream and it wasn’t even that good.
Amazing chocolates. Gianduia with hazelnut is the favorite here.

reviews.text:
Venchi 巧克力月餅禮盒
聽歌時吃一點朱古力
才可以一覺安睡

2款巧克力月餅：
薑配椰絲雙層巧克力月餅 和
伯爵茶雙層巧克力月餅

薑配椰絲雙層巧克力月餅
無麩質餅乾碎，椰絲配搭黑巧克力
56%黑巧克力的外層

伯爵茶雙層巧克力月餅 
上層是伯爵茶白巧克力醬配無麩質餅乾碎
下層黑巧克力，加上56%黑巧克力的外殼
Very nice ice creams there, esp chocolate. My friend bought the hazelnut spread and apparently that’s also very good.

The gelato is life changing!! Chocolate is the best (duh, Captain Obvious).
